- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper proposes a novel iterative method for adapting a graph to image data. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper proposes a method for oversegmenting graphs based on image features. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possibility as the paper proposes a method for image classification using a Deep Geometric Learning architecture, which may involve neural networks.
